ike%20the%20Fair%20and%20Remunerative%20Price%20(FRP)%20for%20sugarcane%20crop%20by%208%25%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20is%20analysed%20to%20be%20of%20not%20much%20help%20to%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708690291000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F14121527%2FF3T6TBIb0AAY7VK.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-at-border-haryana-government-waives-interest-and-penalty-on-crop-loans%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20CM%2C%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%2C%20announced%20the%20move%20while%20speaking%20on%20the%20Rs%201.89%20lakh%20crore%20state%20budget%20for%20the%20FY24-25.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-at-border-haryana-government-waives-interest-and-penalty-on-crop-loans%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Selena%20Gomez%20drops%20fun%20new%20single%20%26quot%3BLove%20On%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708690277000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107945868%2Cimgsize-176522.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fselena-gomez-drops-fun-new-single-love-on-paris-themed-music-video-delights-fans%2Farticleshow%2F107945924.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107945924.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFilming%20the%20video%20in%20Paris%20held%20special%20significance%20for%20Selena%2C%20who%20shared%20glimpses%20of%20her%20time%20in%20the%20city%20while%20working%20on%20the%20project.%20Expressing%20gratitude%20for%20the%20experience%2C%20she%20teased%20her%20upcoming%20film%2C%20Emilia%20Perez%2C%20hinting%20at%20exciting%20developments%20in%20her%20career%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%