ts%20to%20help%20people%20in%20desperate%20need%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20can%20%E2%80%9Conly%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHumanitarian%20workers%2C%20themselves%20displaced%20and%20facing%20shelling%2C%20death%2C%20movement%20restrictions%20and%20a%20breakdown%20of%20civil%20order%2C%20continue%20efforts%20to%20deliver%20to%20those%20in%20need%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%2C%20faced%20with%20so%20many%20obstacles%20%E2%80%93%20including%20safety%20and%20movement%20restrictions%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20only%20do%20so%20much.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20essentials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20principals%20underscored%20that%20no%20amount%20of%20humanitarian%20response%20will%20make%20up%20for%20the%20months%20of%20deprivation%20that%20families%20in%20Gaza%20have%20endured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20our%20effort%20to%20salvage%20the%20humanitarian%20operation%20so%20that%20we%20can%20provide%2C%20at%20the%20very%20least%2C%20the%20bare%20essentials%3A%20medicine%2C%20drinking%20water%2C%20food%20and%20shelter%20as%20temperatures%20plummet%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20that%2C%20they%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%2010%20indispensable%20elements%3A%20an%20immediate%20ceasefire%3B%20protection%20of%20civilians%20and%20civilian%20infrastructure%3B%20immediate%20release%20of%20hostages%3B%20reliable%20entry%20points%20for%20aid%3B%20security%20assurances%20and%20unimpeded%20access%3B%20a%20functioning%20humanitarian%20notification%20system%3B%20roads%20cleared%20of%20explosive%20ordnance%3B%20and%20a%20stable%20communication%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20they%20called%20for%20the%20UN%20agency%20assisting%20Palestine%20refugees%20(%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unrwa.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUNRWA%3C%2Fa%3E)%20to%20receive%20the%20resources%20it%20needs%20to%20provide%20life-saving%20assistance%20as%20well%20as%20a%20halt%20to%20campaigns%20seeking%20to%20discredit%20the%20UN%20and%20NGOs%20doing%20their%20best%20to%20save%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20calling%20on%20Israel%20to%20fulfil%20its%20legal%20obligation%2C%20under%20international%20humanitarian%20and%20human%20rights%20law%2C%20to%20provide%20food%20and%20medical%20supplies%20and%20facilitate%20aid%20operations%2C%20and%20on%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20leaders%20to%20prevent%20an%20even%20worse%20catastrophe%20from%20happening%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20humanitarian%20leaders%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.un.org%2Fen%2Fstory%2F2024%2F02%2F1146837%5C%22%3Epublished%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%3C%2Fem%3E%20UN%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708689616000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F28140819%2FGEw1UHwXMAEPdVM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdiseases-are-rampant-famine-is-looming-humanitarian-leaders-unite-in-urgent-plea-for-gaza%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22'Water%20is%20at%20a%20trickle.%20Basic%20infrastructure%20has%20been%20decimated.%20Food%20production%20has%20come%20to%20a%20halt.%20One%20million%20children%20face%20daily%20traumas%2C'%20said%20the%20principals%20of%20the%20Inter-Agency%20Standing%20Committee%2C%20the%20coordinating%20body%20of%20global%20humanitarian%20organisations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fdiseases-are-rampant-famine-is-looming-humanitarian-leaders-unite-in-urgent-plea-for-gaza%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22California's%20%2420%20minimum%20wage%20for%20fast-food%20workers%20could%20make%20burgers%20and%20chicken%20so%20expensive%20that%20people%20just%20buy%20more%20groceries%20instead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cim