0sluggish%20growth%2C%20its%20per%20capita%20income%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20World%20Bank%20data%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdata.worldbank.org%2Findicator%2FNY.GDP.PCAP.CD%3Flocations%3DPK%5C%22%3Estands%20at%20%241%2C588.9%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20nearly%20double%20that%20of%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20many%20know%20this%20grim%20reality%3A%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20not%20only%20trails%20behind%20Pakistan%20but%20also%20lags%20behind%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%2C%20renowned%20as%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20poorest%20regions.%20World%20Bank%20Open%20Data%20indicates%20Sub-Saharan%20Africa%E2%80%99s%20(excluding%20high%20income)%20per%20capita%20income%20at%20current%20US%24%20is%20%241700.1%20in%202022.%20While%20some%20economists%20argue%20that%20per%20capita%20income%20alone%20fails%20to%20fully%20encapsulate%20a%20region%E2%80%99s%20economic%20standing%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20undeniable%20that%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20economic%20condition%20falls%20significantly%20short%20of%20optimal%20levels.%20For%20example%2C%20Noida%20plays%20a%20big%20role%20in%20increasing%20the%20per%20capita%20income%20of%20UP.%20The%20per%20capita%20income%20simply%20does%20not%20mean%20all%20citizens%20of%20UP%20are%20earning%20Rs%2070%2C792%20per%20year.%20Per%20capita%20income%20is%20calculated%20by%20taking%20the%20ratio%20of%20the%20total%20income%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20total%20population%20of%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fundamental%20flaw%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20economy%20lies%20in%20its%20entrenched%20feudal%20system%2C%20where%20the%20state%20lords%20over%20cattle%2C%20women%2C%20marginalised%20communities%20and%20minorities.%20The%20pervasive%20presence%20of%20the%20so-called%20mafia%20raj%2C%20along%20with%20frequent%20brutalities%20such%20as%20gang%20rape%20and%20violence%2C%20has%20tainted%20UP%E2%80%99s%20reputation.%20Consequently%2C%20when%20the%20chief%20minister%20convenes%20an%20investor%20summit%2C%20prominent%20business%20leaders%20may%20attend%20and%20sign%20Memorandums%20of%20Understanding%2C%20yet%20the%20conversion%20rate%20remains%20abysmal.%20In%20essence%2C%20these%20investors%2C%20gripped%20by%20apprehension%20regarding%20the%20current%20administration%2C%20may%20momentarily%20commit%2C%20but%20they%20rarely%20follow%20through%20with%20the%20initiation%20or%20actualisation%20of%20commercial%20projects%20in%20UP.%20The%20share%20of%20industrial%20sector%20in%20gross%20value%20added%20has%20been%20decreasing.%20From%202012-17%2C%20the%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20the%20industrial%20sector%20has%20been%209.9%25%20and%20from%202017-22%2C%20it%20declined%20to%20a%20mere%200.6%25.%20In%20terms%20of%20number%20of%20factories%2C%20Bihar%20saw%20a%20100.4%25%20increase%2C%20Haryana%20saw%20a%20159%25%20increase%2C%20Assam%20saw%20a%20200%25%20increase%20while%20UP%20saw%20an%20increase%20of%20only%2069%25%20from%20the%20period%202004-05%20to%202019-20.%20The%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20failure%20to%20redistribute%20land%20and%20dismal%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20apparently%20made%20UP%20an%20economic%20wasteland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20facet%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20predicament%20manifests%20in%20the%20relentless%20scourge%20of%20poverty.%20The%20state%20has%20nearly%2023%25%20of%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20Just%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20three%20districts%20of%20UP%20namely%20Bahraich%2C%20Balrampur%2C%20Shravasti%20were%20in%20the%20headlines%20for%20recording%20a%2070%25%20poverty%20rate.%20As%20per%20the%20latest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.niti.gov.in%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2F2023-08%2FIndia-National-Multidimentional-Poverty-Index-2023.pdf%5C%22%3ENITI%20Aayog%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202023%2C%20Bahraich%20has%20more%2050%25%20population%20who%20are%20multidimensionally%20poor.%20The%20state%E2%80%99s%20life%20expectancy%2C%20at%2066%20years%2C%20parallels%20that%20of%20African%20nations%20like%20Ethiopia%20and%20Gabon.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2Fscripts%2FAnnualPublications.aspx%3Fhead%3DHandbook%2Bof%2BStatistics%2Bon%2BIndian%2BStates%5C%22%3ERBI%20Handbook%20of%20Indian%20States%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20infant%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%2038%20per%201%2C000%20in%202020%2C%20the%20maternal%20mortality%20rate%20stands%20at%20167%20per%201%2C00%2C000%20live%20births%20and%2045.6%25%20of%20pregnant%20women%20aged%20between%2015-45%20and%2066%25%20of%20children%20of%20aged%20between%206-59%20months%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressReleasePage.aspx%3FPRID%3D1795421%5C%22%3Eare%20anaemic%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Despite%20the%20touted%20%E2%80%9Cdemographic%20dividend%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20grotesque%20reality%20is%20when%2050.4%25%20of%20the%20female%20population%20aged%20between%2015-49%20years%20are%20anaemic%2C%20the%20prospect%20of%20any%20dividend%20is%20risible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20delve%20into%20the%20growth%20rate.%20The%20chief%20minister%20of%20the%20state%20has%20made%20the%20bold%20claim%20of%20a%20%241%20trillion%20economy.%20It%20is%20conventionally%20believed%20that%20states%20with%20a%20lower%20initial%20economic%20base%20possess%20higher%20potential%20for%20growth.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20poorer%20a%20state%2C%20the%20faster%20it%20can%20advance%20economically%2C%20thereby%20gaining%20increased%20access%20to%20funds%20within%20the%20Indian%20Union.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffrontline.thehindu.com%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-economy-comparison-with-tamil-nadu-south-india%2Farticle67821390.ece%5C%22%3EFor%20example%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20UP%20receives%20Rs%202.73%20back%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union%20of%20India%2C%20while%20Tamil%20Nadu%20receives%20only%2029%20paisa%20for%20every%20Re%201%20it%20contributes%20to%20the%20Union.%20Perhaps%20an%20argument%20could%20be%20made%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20working%20more%20towards%20funding%20the%20freebies%20of%20UP%2C%20but%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20objectivity%2C%20I%20would%20focus%20solely%20on%20UP.%20The%20compound%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Flucknow-news%2Fups-gsdp-shrinks-5-9-per-cent-in-202021-101632161467657.html%5C%22%3EUP%E2%80%99s%20Gross%20State%20Domestic%20Product%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20current%20prices%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Feconomy%2Fdid-up-economy-do-better-under-akhilesh-than-yogi-a-data-check-on-states-1-trillion-ambition%2F1627925%2F%5C%22%3E%20has%20been%208.28%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20period%202016-17%20to%202021-22%2C%20as%20per%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Economics%20and%20Statistics%2C%20GOUP%20(Government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh).%20To%20achieve%20a%20%241%20trillion%20target%20in%20five%20years%2C%20UP%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradesh-election-adityanath-economic-performance%5C%22%3Eneeds%20to%20grow%20by%2032%25%20per%20annum%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20is%20no%20harm%20in%20having%20the%20audacity%20of%20ambition%2C%20but%20truth%20be%20told%2C%20spaceships%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20lit%20up%20by%20candles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lamentable%20part%20of%20UP%E2%80%99s%20story%20is%20that%20the%20voters%20are%20completely%20agnostic%20about%20the%20democratic%20power%20they%20posses%20to%20bring%20in%20an%20economic%20transformation.%20The%20poor%20voters%20are%20failing%20to%20grasp%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20voting%20for%20forces%20that%20are%20further%20disenfranchising%20them.%20The%20result%20of%20this%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fopinion%2Futtar-pradesh-began-declining-after-1980s-old-industrial-cities-played-big-role%2F710784%2F%5C%22%3EUP%20has%20become%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20purgatory%20of%20prosperity%20and%20a%20geography%20of%20maladies.%20The%20economy%20cannot%20be%20drastically%20upscaled%20unless%20there%20is%20massive%20democratic%20reform%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20steady%20shrinkage%20of%20democratic%20spaces%2C%20laceration%20of%20institutional%20autonomy%2C%20the%20focus%20on%20cults%20need%20to%20stop.%20Income%2C%20quality%20of%20living%20needs%20to%20be%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20discourse%20replacing%20caste%20and%20cult.%20In%20a%20conservative%20democratic%20milieu%2C%20any%20hope%20for%20economic%20resurgence%20remains%20futile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESnehasis%20Mukhopadhyay%20is%20a%20data%20science%20enthusiast%20with%20a%20penchant%20for%20drawing%20insights%20from%20political%20economy.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708687802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23160306%2Fprasoon-srivastav-vDfkrGeRXRE-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20complete%20breakdown%20of%20infrastructure%2C%20failure%20to%20redistribute%20land%20and%20dismal%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20has%20made%20UP%20an%20economic%20wasteland.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Futtar-pradeshs-economy-down-the-rabbit-hole-and-beyond%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kamal%20Nath%20Calls%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20%26quot%3BOur%20Leader%26quot%3B%2C%20Urges%20People%20To%20Join%20His%20Yatra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDays%20after%20speculation%20of%20former%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20switching%20sides%20and%20joining%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20on%20Friday%20urged%20the%20people%20and%20the%20workers%20to%20join%20Rahul%20Gandhi-led%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nath%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Congress%20workers%20are%20excited%20to%20welcome%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra.%20Our%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20across%20the%20country%20and%20announced%20a%20decisive%20fight%20against%20injustice%2C%20oppression%20and%20exploitation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20urge%20the%20people%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20state%20Congress%20workers%20to%20become%20the%20strength%20and%20courage%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20by%20joining%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyay%20Yatra%20in%20maximum%20numbers.%20Together%2C%20you%20and%20I%20will%20bring%20this%20great%20campaign%20against%20injustice%20to%20an%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Nath%20made%20headlines%20recently%20over%20speculation%20that%20he%20could%20join%20the%20BJP%20but%2C%20as%20of%20now%2C%20there%20is%20no%20sign%20of%20him%20switching%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speculation%20gained%20momentum%20after%20a%20post%20shared%20by%20former%20Congress%20leader%20and%20BJP%20State%20Spokesperson%20Narendra%20Saluja%20showed%20a%20picture%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20with%20Nakul%20Nath%2C%20captioned%20'Jai%20Shree%20Ram'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20about%20his%20plans%20to%20switch%20sides%2C%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20said%20the%20media%20would%20be%20informed%20%26quot%3Bif%20there%20is%20something.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20are%20you%20all%20getting%20excited%3F%20It%20is%20not%20about%20denying.%20I%20will%20inform%20you%20all%20if%20there%20is%20something%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20to%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2010%2C%20amid%20media%20reports%20and%20speculation%20of%20his%20switch%2C%20Mr%20Nath%20shared%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20affirming%20his%20commitment%20to%20the%20ideology%20of%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ideology%20of%20Congress%20is%20the%20ideology%20of%20truth%2C%20religion%2