0Fattore%20recovered%20quickly%2C%20and%20she%20left%20the%20rehab%20center%20in%20June%202013%2C%20a%20month%20after%20she%20arrived.%20It%20took%20her%20a%20further%20year%20to%20fully%20recover%20and%20come%20off%20her%20anti-clotting%20medications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFattore%20will%20have%20to%20take%20seizure%20medications%20for%20life%2C%20but%20she%20has%20been%20able%20to%20move%20across%20the%20country%20and%20return%20to%20normality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marissa%20Fattore%20rock%20climbing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d87d66ce7f1785b2e35a9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFattore%20rock%20climbing%20after%20recovering%20from%20her%20stroke.%3Cp%3EMarissa%20Fattore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3ESymptoms%20of%20stroke%20include%20weakness%20on%20one%20side%20of%20the%20body%20and%20a%20severe%20headache%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20her%20stroke%2C%20Fattore%20has%20implemented%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F8-simple-habits-add-decades-onto-to-your-life-research-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elifestyle%20changes%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maintain%20a%20healthy%20cardiovascular%20system%2C%20including%20staying%20active%3B%20eating%20a%20healthy%20diet%20full%20of%20whole%20grains%2C%20lean%20proteins%2C%20fruits%2C%20and%20vegetables%3B%20not%20smoking%3B%20getting%20eight%20hours%20of%20sleep%20a%20night%3B%20and%20monitoring%20her%20blood%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wants%20people%20to%20know%20that%20cardiovascular%20disease%20can%20happen%20to%20anyone%20and%20that%20learning%20the%20warning%20signs%20could%20help%20save%20a%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpotting%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-mom-stroke-mistaken-for-ear-infection-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esigns%20of%20a%20stroke%3C%2Fa%3E%20early%20and%20acting%2