o%20track%20your%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20success%20for%20us%20was%20tracking%20every%20dollar%20spent.%20Seeing%20where%20our%20money%20went%20gave%20us%20a%20better%20idea%20of%20how%20much%20was%20wasted%20each%20month%20on%20apps%20we%20didn't%20need%20or%20rarely%20used%2C%20helping%20us%20save%20hundreds%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E2.%20Categorize%20all%20your%20subscriptions%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221921%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Peloton%20Bike%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5e56e2e0fee23d4beb1f8558%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221171%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20Peloton%20subscription%20passed%20a%20key%20test.%3Cp%3EPeloton%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20broke%20all%20our%20subscriptions%20into%20three%20categories%3A%20needs%2C%20wants%2C%20and%20why%20are%20we%20still%20paying%20for%20this%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20something%20to%20be%20a%20need%2C%20it%20had%20to%20either%20make%20us%20happier%2C%20healthier%2C%20or%20wealthier.%20For%20example%2C%20watching%20sports%20makes%20me%20happy%2C%20so%20ESPN%2B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20which%20costs%20%2411%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eis%20in.%20The%20Peloton%20app%20%E2%80%94%20which%20costs%20%2448%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Emakes%20us%20physically%20and%20mentally%20healthier%2C%20so%20it%20is%20a%20need.%20We%20also%20kept%20the%20YNAB%20app%20%E2%80%94%20which%20costs%20%2499%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20because%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20it%20saves%20us%20makes%20up%20for%20the%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20%E2%80%94%20which%20starts%20at%20%247%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20good%20example%20of%20one%20of%20our%20wants.%20We%20watch%20Netflix%20sometimes%2C%20but%20some%20months%20go%20by%20without%20it%20being%20used.%20So%20this%20is%20a%20subscription%20that%20we%20will%20pause%20for%20a%20while%20and%20then%20pick%20back%20up%20for%20a%20month%20or%20two%20and%20then%20pause%20again.%20We%20were%20surprised%20by%20how%20often%20we%20went%20five%20or%20six%20months%20without%20needing%20to%20see%20anything%20on%20certain%20streaming%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20last%20category%2C%20it%20can%20be%20annoying%20to%20cancel%20unwanted%20subscriptions%2C%20but%20many%20companies%20are%20making%20it%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E3.%20Avoid%20annual%20subscriptions%2C%20if%20possible%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222460%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22HBO%20Max%20subscription%20plans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d76fbfa3bd891424f93bc0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221156%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20annual%20subscription%20can%20save%20you%2020%25%20on%20HBO%20Max%2C%20but%20only%20if%20you%20use%20it%20all%20the%20time.%3Cp%3EHBO%20Max%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnnual%20subscriptions%20are%20enticing%20because%20they%20cost%20less%20in%20the%20long%20run%2C%20but%20there%20is%20a%20reason%20for%20that%20%E2%80%94%20the%20companies%20want%20to%20lock%20you%20in%20long-term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20with%20annual%20subscriptions%20is%20that%20you%20lose%20flexibility%20and%20control%2C%20and%20that%20is%20the%20key%20to%20saving%20the%20most%20money%2C%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20can%20stay%20disciplined%20and%20review%20your%20monthly%20subscriptions%20every%20month%20or%20two%20and%20pause%20or%20cancel%20the%20ones%20you%20don't%20need%2C%20it%20usually%20only%20takes%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20with%20the%20subscription%20off%20to%20save%20money%20over%20the%20annual%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20there%20are%20exceptions.%20I%20have%20journaling%2C%20exercise%2C%20and%20banking%20apps%20I%20use%20every%20day%20without%20fail.%20In%20those%20cases%2C%20it%20does%20make%20sense%20to%20go%20with%20the%20annual%20plans.%20In%20addition%2C%20there%20are%20occasionally%20annual%20deals%20that%20are%20just%20too%20good%20to%20pass%20up.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmashable.com%2Farticle%2Fnov-25-paramount-plus-black-friday-cyber-monday-deal%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParamount%2B%20Cyber%20Monday%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20an%20annual%20subscription%20for%20%2424%20or%20%242%20a%20month.%20It%20would%20take%20just%20four%20months%20to%20pay%20the%20same%20amount%20under%20the%20monthly%20%246%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E4.%20Avoid%20bundles%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%20Bundle%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7709cf533b039a885f890%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EConsider%20how%20often%20you%20need%20all%20the%20apps%20before%20signing%20up%20for%20a%20bundle.%3Cp%3EDisney%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAvoiding%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-streaming-app-disney-warner-fox-pay-cable-tv-nfl-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebundles%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20another%20strategy%20that%20keeps%20your%20sub%3Cs%3Es%3C%2Fs%3Ecriptions%20flexible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20I%20use%20ESPN%2B%20almost%20daily%20and%20Disney%2B%20occasionally.%20If%20you%20subscribe%20to%20those%20apps%20separately%2C%20it%20would%20cost%20%2419%20a%20month.%20It%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20good%20deal%20to%20get%20the%20bundle%20at%20%2415%20a%20month%2C%20which%20also%20comes%20with%20Hulu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20we%20never%20use%20Hulu%2C%20and%20the%20bundle%20takes%20away%20our%20flexibility%20to%20turn%20off%20Disney%2B%20for%20those%20stretches%20of%20months%20when%20there%20is%20nothing%20on%20there%20we%20want%20to%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bundle%20would%20have%20cost%20us%20%24180%20in%202023.%20Instead%2C%20we%20kept%20ESPN%2B%20all%20year%20and%20used%20Disney%2B%20for%20two%20months%20which%20cost%20%24148%2C%20a%20savings%20of%20%2432.%20Not%20the%20biggest%20savings%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20it%20adds%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E5.%20Always%20cancel%20your%20subscriptions%20immediately%2C%20even%20if%20you%20plan%20to%20keep%20it%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221559%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20iOS%20subscriptions%20page%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d77d7ef533b039a88600b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221169%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20iOS%20subscriptions%20page.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20suggest%20canceling%20any%20subscription%20you%20buy.%20That%20helps%20control%20your%20spending%20as%20you%20decide%20when%20%E2%80%94%20and%20if%20%E2%80%94%20you%20will%20renew%20the%20subscription.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20also%20key%20for%20those%20free%20trials%2C%20which%20often%20come%20with%20automatic%20subscriptions%20when%20the%20trial%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20will%20be%20amazed%20at%20how%20often%20you%20can%20go%20weeks%20or%20months%20without%20using%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E6.%20Don't%20assume%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeal%26quot%3B%20you%20are%20being%20offered%20is%20the%20best%20one%20available%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple%20iOS%20subscription%20plans%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d773ccf533b039a885fac5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20subscriptions%20being%20offered%20can%20vary%20and%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20settings.%3Cp%3ECork%20Gaines%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Apple%20iOS%20devices%2C%20there%20is%20a%20subscription%20trick%20for%20finding%20the%20best%20deal%20for%20an%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20here%20is%20to%20cancel%20the%20subscription.%20After%20that%2C%20go%20into%20the%20subscription%20section%20under%20settings.%20Here%20you%20will%20find%20every%20app%20you%20have%20or%20had%20a%20subscription%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClick%20on%20the%20app%3Cstrong%3E%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20and%20on%20the%20next%20page%2C%20there%20is%20an%20option%20to%20%26quot%3Bsee%20all%20plans.%26quot%3B%20Here%2C%20the%20app%20must%20list%20all%20its%20available%20subscriptions%2C%20not%20just%20those%20advertised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20offers%20can%20vary%20widely%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20we've%20found%20a%20better%20deal%20roughly%2050%25%20of%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20our%20subscriptions%20under%20control%20was%20a%20bit%20overwhelming%20at%20first%2C%20and%20still%20takes%20a%20little%20leg%20work%20every%20month%20to%20keep%20on%20top%20of%20them.%20But%20the%20savings%20is%20worth%20the%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-manage-app-subscriptions-save-money-monthly-vs-annual-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708686181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d77a6ca3bd891424f94204%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-manage-app-subscriptions-save-money-monthly-vs-annual-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20family%20of%20four%20is%20saving%20about%20%24190%20a%20month%20by%20managing%20our%20app%20subscriptions.%20Here%20are%20the%206%20steps%20we%20took%20to%20rein%20in%20our%20monthly%20costs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cgaines%40insider.com%20(Cork%20Gaines)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-manage-app-subscriptions-save-money-monthly-vs-annual-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2210%20things%20to%20stream%20this%20weekend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2