com%2Fgen-z-9-to-5-tiring-tips-work-life-balance-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Removing%20Secularism%20Will%20Sound%20the%20Death%20Knell%20of%20Democracy%E2%80%99%3A%20Former%20SC%20Judge%20Justice%20K.M.%20Joseph%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23153316%2Fimage-1861.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20K.M.%20Joseph%20has%20said%20that%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%20is%20indispensable%20in%20a%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20if%20you%20take%20away%20secularism%20from%20the%20preamble%2C%20none%20of%20the%20features%20of%20secularism%20would%20go%20away.%20So%20you%20cannot%20take%20away%20Secularism%20from%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecularism%20is%20absolutely%20indispensable%20in%20a%20democracy.%20If%20secularism%20is%20going%20to%20be%20removed%20by%20any%20government%20from%20the%20Preamble%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20under%20the%20impression%20that%20by%20merely%20removing%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%2C%20you%20are%20removing%20the%20features%20of%20secularism%E2%80%A6even%20if%20it%20is%20removed%2C%20it%20will%20sound%20the%20death%20knell%20of%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20made%20these%20remarks%20while%20delivering%20a%20lecture%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20by%20the%20Kerala%20High%20Court%20Advocates%20Association.%20The%20lecture%20was%20titled%20%E2%80%98The%20Concept%20of%20Secularism%20under%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fif-any-govt-removes-secularism-from-preamble-it-will-sound-death-knell-of-democracy-justice-km-joseph-250240%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20calls%20from%20certain%20quarters%20to%20remove%20the%20reference%20to%20%E2%80%98secularism%E2%80%99%20from%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecularism%20is%20a%20facet%20of%20equality.%20If%20you%20treat%20all%20religions%20equally%2C%20that%20is%20secularism.%20You%20are%20fair%2C%20you%20do%20not%20bias%20or%20patronise.%20This%20is%20substance%20as%20held%20in%20S.R.%20Bommai%20%5Bjudgment%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20that%20religion%20is%20your%20private%20affair%2C%20keep%20it%20private%E2%80%A6%5Bthe%5D%20State%20must%20maintain%20complete%20neutrality.%20This%20is%20the%20substance%20of%20what%20is%20laid%20down%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20these%20batch%20of%20cases%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20members%20of%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20agreed%20that%20India%20is%20a%20secular%20country%2C%20they%20felt%20that%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20specifically%20mention%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20this%20context.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20agreement%20particularly%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20partition%2C%20which%20saw%20the%20birth%20of%20Pakistan%20choosing%20a%20theocratic%20model%2C%20that%20India%20would%20be%20a%20secular%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnity%20in%20diversity%20does%20not%20mean%20you%20can%20wipe%20out%20diversity.%20It%20cannot%20mean%20you%20will%20achieve%20unity%20by%20wiping%20out%20diversity%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20secularism%2C%20it%20is%20the%20bounden%20duty%20of%20the%20State%20to%20protect%20the%20lives%20of%20all%20its%20citizens%20regardless%20of%20religion%2C%20race%2C%20caste%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%20functionary%2C%20no%20representative%2C%20no%20minister%20can%20endorse%20any%20religion%2C%20can%20take%20sides%20in%20a%20fight%20between%20religions.%20That%20leads%20to%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20other%20religions%20are%20secondary%2C%20which%20is%20not%20because%20all%20religions%20under%20the%20principle%20of%20secularism%20must%20be%20treated%20equally%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWdxxlOP4IpA%3Fsi%3D6zxFoKgRj-jfn2OV%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20that%20citizens%20must%20rise%20to%20protect%20secularism%20and%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20point%20in%20lying%20in%20bed%20saying%20I%20will%20not%20protest%20or%20do%20anything%2C%20let%20the%20State%20do%20whatever%20it%20wants.%20You%20mount%20all%20sorts%20of%20criticism%20and%20display%20complete%20impotence%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20your%20own%20actions.%20What%20is%20it%20that%20you%E2%80%99re%20contributing%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20he%20mentioned%20the%20fundamental%20duties%20of%20the%20citizens%20enshrined%20under%20Article%2051A%20of%20the%20Constitution%2C%20particularly%20the%20need%20to%20cultivate%20a%20scientific%20temper%20and%20feeling%20of%20fraternity%20rising%20above%20religions%20and%20other%20divisions%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressed%20hope%20that%20secularism%20will%20survive%20in%20India%2C%20Justice%20Joseph%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20still%20optimistic%20that%20secularism%20will%20survive.%20My%20optimism%20comes%20largely%20from%20the%20catholicity%20of%20the%20Hindu%20religion%20itself.%20The%20vast%20majority%20of%20the%20Hindus%20are%20completely%20broadminded%20and%20tolerant%20and%20they%20do%20not%20treat%20religion%20in%20the%20manner%20religion%20is%20treated%20in%20other%20religions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20shores%20of%20this%20country%20were%20opened%20to%20other%20religions%2C%20including%20Christianity%20and%20Islam%20when%20there%20was%20no%20war.%20When%20Islam%20came%20in%208th%20century%2C%20they%20came%20as%20traders.%20When%20Christianity%20came%2C%20there%20was%20no%20army%20marching%20by%20their%20side.%20The%20shores%20of%20the%20country%20were%20thrown%20open%20by%20the%20kings%2C%20the%20priests%E2%80%A6Hinduism%20is%20essentially%20based%20on%20the%20quest%20for%20universal%20truth%20at%20the%20highest%20level%E2%80%A6in%20Hinduism%20you%20will%20find%20the%20dualism%20of%20Madhavacharya%2C%20non-dualism%20of%20Shankaracharya%E2%80%A6so%20the%20very%20innate%20faith%20which%20Hinduism%20is%20such%20that%20it%20is%20broadminded%20to%20absorb%20other%20faiths.%20The%20problem%20arises%20when%20it%20is%20abused%2C%20misused%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20politics%2C%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20gaining%20power.%20That%20is%20where%20the%20greatest%20danger%20lies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708686010000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F23153316%2Fimage-1861.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fremoving-secularism-will-sound-the-death-knell-of-democracy-former-sc-judge-justice-k-m-joseph%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20whole%20idea%20of%20secularism%20is%20that%20religion%20is%20your%20private%20affair%2C%20keep%20it%20private%E2%80%A6%5Bthe%5D%20State%20must%20maintain%20complete%20neutrality%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Justice%20Joseph.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fremoving-secularism-will-sound-the-death-knell-of-democracy-former-sc-judge-justice-k-m-joseph%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mortgage%20Interest%20Rates%20Today%2C%20February%2023%2C%202024%20%7C%20Rates%20Are%20Now%20Closer%20to%207%25%20Than%20They've%20Been%20in%20Months%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20answer%20readers'%20home-buying%20questions%20and%2