0the%20scammers%20the%20details.%20The%20YouTuber%20also%20keeps%20them%20online%20for%20hours%20at%20a%20time%2C%20playing%20along%20with%20their%20scams.%20He%20drives%20them%20crazy%20by%20responding%20slowly%20and%20stupidly%20to%20their%20demands.%20%26quot%3BNeld%26quot%3B%20said%20that%20the%20scammers%20usually%20pretend%20to%20be%20American%20or%20Mexican%2C%20with%20names%20such%20as%20Thomas%20Wayne%20and%20Brian%20Collins.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhe-eavesdropped-on-wifes-calls-during-wfh-gets-insider-trading-charge-5111008%5C%22%3EUS%20Man%20Makes%20%242%20Million%20By%20Eavesdropping%20On%20Wife's%20Office%20Calls%20During%20WFH%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20worn%20down%20some%20to%20the%20point%20of%20tears%2C%20swearing%20they%20will%20give%20up%20their%20criminality%20and%20go%20straight%20if%20he'd%20only%20leave%20them%20alone%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20%26quot%3BNeld%26quot%3B%20insider%20told%20The%20%3Cem%3EPost%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20usually%20happens%20only%20after%20he's%20actually%20hacked%20their%20computers%20and%20downloaded%20or%20destroyed%20all%20of%20their%20data%20by%20installing%20a%20very%20dangerous%20computer%20virus%20on%20the%20scammers'%20computers%2C%20gained%20control%20of%20their%20webcams%20and%20livestreamed%20video%20of%20them%20to%20the%20world%2C%20embarrassing%20them%20publicly%20and%20threatening%20to%20contact%20their%20innocent%20families%2C%20revealing%20their%20criminal%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20brilliant%20and%20has%20a%20truly%20dark%20sense%20of%20humor.%20While%20he%20won't%20discuss%20it%2C%20he%20does%20report%20some%20of%20his%20investigations%20to%20authorities%20in%20the%20US%20and%20in%20India%2C%20in%20hopes%20authorities%20will%20make%20arrests%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20source%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20You