nhance-cooperation-between-india-and-italy-124022300575_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfc-partners-with-sace-to-enhance-cooperation-between-india-and-italy-124022300575_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Everything%20is%20getting%20worse'%3A%20Fatigue%20marks%20Ukraine%20war%20anniversary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708684027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107942834%2Cimgsize-1374143.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feverything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary%2Farticleshow%2F107942660.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107942660.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feverything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary%2Farticleshow%2F107942660.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feverything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107942660.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Feverything-is-getting-worse-fatigue-marks-ukraine-war-anniversary%2Famp_articleshow%2F107942660.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20may%20look%20like%20Trump%20scared%20NATO%20back%20into%20readiness%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it's%20probably%20all%20down%20to%20Putin%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224194%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trump%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c9236f6fcb546d2d4e5f82%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222796%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaks%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Conway%2C%20S.C.%2C%20on%20February%2010%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EAP%20Photo%2FManuel%20Balce%20Ceneta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20shocked%20NATO%20by%20seemingly%20encouraging%20an%20attack%20on%20members%20that%20don't%20meet%20spending%20targets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20leaders%20have%20rushed%20to%20make%20defense%20deals%20and%20increase%20their%20military%20contributions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20it's%20not%20really%20to%20do%20with%20Trump%2C%20and%20his%20threats%20have%20no%20real%20%26quot%3Bsilver%20lining%2C%26quot%3B%20experts%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Trump%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20he'd%20encourage%20Russia%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20whatever%20the%20hell%20they%20want%26quot%3B%20to%20NATO%20countries%20that%20don't%20meet%20defense%20spending%20expectations%2C%20world%20leaders%20reacted%20in%20shock.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-trump-nato-russia-comments-appalling-unhinged-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecalled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20remarks%20%26quot%3Bunhinged%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20NATO's%20secretary-general%20said%20they%20made%20both%20US%20and%20European%20soldiers%20less%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20some%20have%20suggested%20that%20%E2%80%94%20like%20it%20or%20not%20%E2%80%94%20the%20prospect%20of%20having%20to%20defend%20themselves%20without%20the%20US%20by%20their%20side%20could%20at%20least%20prompt%20some%20NATO%20members%20to%20ratchet%20up%20much-needed%20spending%20on%20their%20militaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEstonia's%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Kaja%20Kallas%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Festonias-pm-says-trumps-nato-comments-should-be-wake-up-call-allies-invest-2024-02-12%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20remarks%20could%20%26quot%3Bmaybe%20wake%20up%20some%20of%20the%20allies%20who%20haven't%20done%20that%20much.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Dutch%20Prime%20Minister%20Mark%20Rutte%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.euractiv.com%2Fsection%2Fdefence-and-security%2Finterview%2Flets-mind-our-own-defence-not-who-sits-in-the-white-house-dutch-pm-rutte-tells-europe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20told%20fellow%20leaders%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20stop%20%26quot%3Bwhining%26quot%3B%20about%20Trump%20and%20start%20investing%20in%20their%20militaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bsilver%20lining%26quot%3B%20of%20boosted%20NATO%20defense%20emerging%20from%20Trump's%20pointed%20remarks%20is%20%26quot%3Bnaive%20or%20delusional%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Edward%20Hunter%20Christie%2C%20a%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Finnish%20Institute%20of%20International%20Affairs%20and%20a%20former%20NATO%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20states'%20increased%20defense%20spending%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20little%20to%20do%20with%20Trump%2C%20experts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETrump%20was%20already%20pushing%20at%20an%20open%20door%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20boasted%20that%20he%20alone%20fixed%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20them%20to%20pay%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20his%20supporters%20at%20the%20same%20rally.%20%26quot%3BNATO%20was%20busted%20until%20I%20came%20along.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20never%20saw%20more%20money%20pour%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20spending%20has%20indeed%20accelerated%20since%20Trump%20entered%20politics.%20As%20of%20last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nato.int%2Fcps%2Fen%2Fnatohq%2Ftopics_67655.htm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E18%20of%20NATO's%2031%20member%20states%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20recommended%20threshold%20of%20spending%202%25%20of%20GDP%20on%20defense.%20That's%20compared%20to%20just%20three%20nations%20back%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20biggest%20driver%20of%20this%20flurry%20is%20almost%20certainly%20not%20Trump%2C%20experts%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretty%20much%20all%20of%20the%20increases%2C%20I%20would%20say%2C%20since%202014%20are%20a%20response%20to%20Russia%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hunter%20Christie.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilliam%20Alberque%2C%20a%20former%20NATO%20arms%20control%20expert%20and%20now%20director%20of%20strategy%2C%20technology%20and%20arms%20control%20at%20the%20International%20Institute%20for%20Strategic%20Studies%2C%20said%20that%20if%20Russia%20hadn't%20annexed%20Crimea%20in%202014%2C%20and%20if%20it%20hadn't%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%202022%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20would%20be%20on%20a%20completely%20different%20glide%20path%20in%20terms%20of%20NATO%20spending%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20angry%20Trump%20got.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlberque%20said%20some%20officials%20may%20be%20quietly%20pleased%20at%20the%20external%20pressure%20from%20Trump%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20scapegoat%20him%20for%20their%20already-planned%20spending%20decisions%20to%20their%20citizens.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20useful%20to%20blame%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20those%20politics%20can%20work%20in%20reverse%20%E2%80%94%20leaders%20that%20had%20planned%20to%20spend%20more%20may%20end%20up%20being%20so%20annoyed%20at%20the%20pressure%20that%20they%20reverse%20course%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPutting%20allies%20under%20pressure%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20bad%20instinct%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20way%20he's%20doing%20it%3F%20An%20awful%20instinct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EIt%20ain't%20what%20you%20do%2C%20it's%20the%20way%20that%20you%20do%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20demands%20of%20NATO%20allies%20also%20weren't%20a%20departure%20from%20existing%20US%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20percentage%20thing%20has%20been%20going%20on%20forever%20and%20ever%20and%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20Alberque%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20there's%20always%20just%20the%20general%20impression%20that%20the%20Europeans%20aren't%20quite%20doing%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Patrick%20Bury%2C%20a%20former%20NATO%20analyst%20and%20now%20a%20lecturer%20in%20international%20security%20at%20the%20UK's%20University%20of%20Bath%2C%20the%20demand%20that%20European%20countries%20pay%20more%20for%20collective%20defense%20isn't%20unreasonable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20an%20%26quot%3Banger%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20US%20over%20it%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThese%20are%20allies%20that%20sent%20generations%20of%20their%20young%20men%20to%20bail%20out%20Europe%2C%20twice%20in%20the%20last%20hundred%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%2C%20Alberque%20said%2C%20is%20%3Cem%3Ehow%3C%2Fem%3E%20Trump%20relates%20to%20the%20alliance%20%E2%80%94%20purely%20transactionally%2C%20and%20with%20poor%20communication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20Trump%20abruptly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.armscontrol.org%2Fact%2F2018-11%2Fnews%2Ftrump-withdraw-us-inf-treaty%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epulled%20the%20US%20from%20a%20key%20nuclear%20arms-control%20treaty%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20move%20was%20in%20line%20with%20the%20policy%20of%20President%20Barack%20Obama%2C%20Alberque%20said.%20The%20problem%20is%20how%20he%20went%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20just%20announced%20it%20one%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20preview%20it%20with%20any%20of%20the%20nations.%20He%20didn't%20get%20them%20ready.%20He%20just%20dropped%20it%20one%20day%20and%20it%20made%20everyone%20scramble%20around%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20meant%20it%20%26quot%3Bjust%20rankled%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20even%20with%20the%20nations%20who%20agreed%20with%20the%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20framing%20the%20NATO%20spending%20demand%20so%20transactionally%2C%20Trump%20did%20%26quot%3Blasting%20damage%26quot%3B%20to%20US%20relations%20with%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20%E2%80%94%20which%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20was%20left%20to%20rebuild%2C%20Alberque%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThreatening%20partners%20is%20%26quot%3Bbananas%26quot%3B%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20transactional%20take%20on%20NATO%20collective%20defense%20is%20ultimately%20reasonable%2C%20Bury%20said%20%E2%80%94%20but%20encouraging%20other%20countries%20to%20attack%20NATO%20allies%20is%20%26quot%3Bbananas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20there's%20some%20reassessments%20going%20on%26quot%3B%20among%20the%20US'%20allies%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20US%20allies%20are%20spending%20more%20money%20on%20NATO%20defense%2C%20it's%20not%20because%20Trump%20is%20goading%20them%2C%20but%20because%20they're%20concerned%20about%20increasing%20global%20instability.%20And%20one%20of%20the%20drivers%20of%20that%20instability%20is%20Trump.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnything%20he%20says%20that%20threatens%20US%20future%20alliances%20is%20going%20to%20make%20countries%20want%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20defense%20because%20they're%20no%20longer%20able%20to%20rely%20on%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20Alberque.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20spending%20increased%20because%20Trump%20demanded%20it%20would%20be%20wrong%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%2C%20no%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20because%20you're%20a%20jackass.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fundamentally%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20he's%20trying%20to%20make%20the%20US%20less%20trustworthy%20as%20an%20ally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20%26quot%3Bwarning%20shot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20Not%20only%20that%20NATO%20countries%20should%20spend%20more%2C%20but%20also%20that%2C%20should%20Trump%20once%20again%20lead%20the%20US%2C%20he%20could%20easily%20make%20agreements%20with%20Russia%20that%20are%20detrimental%20to%20European%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlberque%20pointed%20to%20current%20GOP%20efforts%20%E2%80%94%20under%20Trump's%20influence%20%E2%80%94%20to%20halt%20further%20funding%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20a%20move%20that%20could%20only%20embolden%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20in%20the%20face%20of%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20prospect%20of%20the%20US%20potentially%20aiding%20Europe's%20biggest%20threat%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0Russia%20%E2%80%94%20is%20what%20has%20other%20world%20leaders%20most%20on%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHunter%20Christie%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20we%20have%20a%20highly%20dangerous%20situation%20and%20that%20Trump%20would%20be%20a%20grave%20danger%20to%20the%20future%20of%20the%20transatlantic%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20is%20actually%20an%20extremely%20negative%20development%20for%20European%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-didnt-scare-nato-defense-spending-putin-did-experts-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708684025000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c9238f917a1dae02455bb7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-didnt-scare-nato-defense-spending-putin-did-experts-2024-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trump's%20eye-opening%20remarks%20encouraging%20Russia%20to%20attack%20NATO%20states%20that%20don't%20meet%20defense%20spending%20targets%20has%20no%20silver%20lining%2C%20experts%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-didnt-scare-nato-defense-spending-putin-did-experts-2024-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20this%20US%20man%20made%20%242%20million%20after%20overhearing%20wife's%20office%20calls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708683922000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107944448%2Cimgsize-62