Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-living-in-denver-moving-from-nyc-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Denver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20colleague%20shared%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20of%20a%20copyeditor%20whose%20background%20matched%20the%20description%20of%20a%20local%20job%20posting%20I'd%20seen%20that%20day.%20I%20looked%20up%20the%20company%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20scrolled%20through%20the%20Denver%20employees%20to%20find%20the%20hiring%20manager.%20That's%20when%20I%20found%20Nick%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20company's%20Denver%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20clicked%20Connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20he%20accepted%20my%20request%20and%20I%20pitched%20the%20copyeditor%20my%20colleague%20had%20met.%20Based%20on%20Nick's%20profile%2C%20he%20appeared%20to%20be%20from%20the%20UK%20and%20new%20to%20Denver.%20I%20ended%20my%20message%20with%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20look%20like%20you're%20from%20here.%20I%20hope%20you're%20enjoying%20it!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22395%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screenshot%20of%20message%20Katie%20sent%20to%20her%20now-husband%2C%20Nick.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7a9b890413ab8e1d62c5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22564%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20LinkedIn%20message%20that%20started%20it%20all.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Doble%2FLinkedIn%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20thrilled%20to%20find%20a%20response%20from%20Nick%20a%20couple%20of%20days%20later.%20He%20didn't%20need%20help%20filling%20the%20role%2C%20but%20he%20asked%3A%20%26quot%3BHow%20long%20have%20you%20called%20Denver%20home%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThus%20began%20a%20series%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-users-sliding-others-dms-tiktoker-dating-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esemi-flirtatious%20LinkedIn%20exchanges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20After%20about%20four%20messages%20back%20and%20forth%2C%20I%20signed%20off%20with%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20ever%20want%20to%20grab%20a%20coffee%20or%20a%20beer%2C%20I%20love%20networking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20later%20found%20out%20that%20after%20reading%20this%2C%20Nick%20announced%20to%20one%20of%20his%20coworkers%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20I've%20just%20gotten%20a%20date%20off%20of%20LinkedIn.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20couldn't%20tell%20if%20it%20was%20networking%20or%20a%20date%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20planned%20to%20meet%20on%20a%20Saturday%20afternoon%20at%20a%20trendy%20cocktail%20bar%20in%20Downtown%20Denver.%20This%20meeting%20felt%20familiar%20and%20different%20at%20the%20same%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0after%20all%2C%20I%20often%20meet%20first-time%20clients%20for%20a%20coffee%20or%20a%20beer%2C%20although%20it%20was%20usually%20the%20former%20and%20never%20on%20a%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20texted%20him%20on%20my%20way%20there%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20wearing%20a%20red-orange%20jacket.%26quot%3B%20He%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20wearing%20a%20claret%20and%20blue%20checkered%20shirt.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20gay%20stepbrother%20once%20informed%20me%20that%20if%20a%20guy%20uses%20a%20color%20outside%20the%20basic%20Crayola%20box%2C%20he's%20gay.%20I%20wasn't%20even%20certain%20what%20%26quot%3Bclaret%26quot%3B%20was.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20nervous%2C%20but%20this%20exchange%20diffused%20the%20situation%20for%20me.%20I%20mean%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-relationship-met-linkedin-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20met%20this%20guy%20on%20LinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20What%20were%20his%20expectations%3F%20What%20were%20mine%3F%20Remembering%20that%20I%20knew%20little%20of%20this%20person%2C%20including%20his%20sexual%20orientation%2C%20brought%20it%20back%20to%20the%20reason%20I%20was%20happy%20to%20be%20there%20%E2%80%94%20I%20love%20meeting%20new%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20walked%20in%2C%20with%20his%20very%20long%20torso%2C%20legs%20for%20days%2C%20and%20darling%20chin%20dimple%20peeking%20out%20from%20under%20his%20short%20beard.%20%3Cem%3EPlease%20don't%20be%20gay%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20thought%2C%20smiling%20as%20we%20made%20eye%20contact%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20that%20claret%20is%20actually%20just%20burgundy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ordered%20drinks%2C%20and%20the%20conversation%20flowed%20effortlessly%20as%20we%20talked%20about%20our%20jobs%2C%20family%2C%20and%20where%20we%20were%20from.%20He%20told%20me%20claret%20and%20blue%20were%20the%20colors%20of%20the%20football%20team%20he%20supported%20back%20home%2C%20West%20Ham%20United.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20us%20stopped%20smiling%20the%20entire%20evening.%20There%20they%20were%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20sparks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBringing%20up%20the%20cancer%20conversation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20several%20months%2C%20one%20thing%20that%20hindered%20my%20dating%20experiences%20was%20that%20I%20had%20been%20diagnosed%20with%20and%20treated%20for%20uveal%20melanoma%2C%20a%20rare%20cancer%20that%20starts%20in%20the%20eye.%20Thankfully%2C%20it%20had%20been%20contained%20in%20my%20eyeball%2C%20and%20a%20biopsy%20of%20the%20cells%20revealed%20a%20less%20than%202%25%20chance%20that%20it%20would%20spread.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20trying%20to%20keep%20this%20part%20of%20me%20under%20wraps%2C%20as%20the%20first%20dates%20where%20I%20had%20revealed%20this%20information%20brought%20blank%20stares.%20One%20guy%20had%20even%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BYour%20current%20situation%20isn't%20conducive%20to%20starting%20a%20romantic%20relationship%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20suggested%20that%20I%20reach%20out%20to%20him%20when%20I%20was%20healthy%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToward%20the%20end%20of%20our%20%26quot%3Bnetworking%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20let%20it%20slip%20to%20Nick%20that%20I%20had%20just%20sold%20my%20scooter%2C%20which%20seemed%20to%20disappoint%20him.%20I%20explained%20that%20cancer%20had%20caused%20full%20blindness%20in%20my%20left%20eye%2C%20making%20it%20too%20dangerous%20to%20ride.%20I%20held%20my%20breath%20and%20waited%20for%20him%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCan%20we%20go%20back%20to%20the%20scooter%3F%20What%20was%20it%20like%20to%20have%20to%20sell%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20clearly%20more%20upset%20that%20I%20no%20longer%20had%20my%20cool%20red%20scooter%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20I%20once%20had%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20exhaled%20in%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20bartender%20presented%20the%20bill%2C%20Nick%20grabbed%20it%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20be%20much%20of%20a%20gentleman%20if%20I%20let%20you%20pay.%26quot%3B%20He%20asked%20if%20he%20could%20see%20me%20again%20as%20he%20handed%20his%20credit%20card%20to%20the%20bartender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOK%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20thought.%20%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20networking%20event.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20left%20the%20restaurant%20and%20walked%20through%20a%20narrow%20path%20to%20get%20to%20the%20street%20corner%2C%20where%20we%20would%20say%20goodbye.%20He%20could%20tell%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20see%2C%20so%20he%20grabbed%20my%20hand.%20When%20we%20got%20to%20the%20corner%2C%20we%20kissed.%20To%20this%20day%2C%20we%20argue%20about%20who%20leaned%20in%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20spend%20my%20life%20with%20him%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%2C%20we%20were%20spending%20all%20our%20time%20together.%20In%20the%20next%20year%2C%20we%20met%20each%20other's%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20traveled%20internationally%2C%20and%20made%20plans%20for%20the%20future.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhen-do-you-know-when-youre-in-love-2017-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20knew%20within%20weeks%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20was%20the%20person%20I'd%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20life%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nick%20and%20Katie%20smiling%20at%20the%20camera.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7b2c96080194819f987cf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%2C%20wearing%20the%20claret%20and%20blue%20shirt%2C%20spent%20Thanksgiving%202013%20with%20Katie.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Ortman%20Doble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20invited%20my%20sisters%20to%20go%20ring%20shopping%20with%20him%20shortly%20after%20we%20celebrated%20one%20year%20of%20dating.%20They%20mapped%20out%20an%20elaborate%20plan%20that%20involved%20him%20proposing%20in%20front%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20on%20Thanksgiving%20Day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20liver%20hijacked%20Nick's%20plans.%20Despite%20the%202%25%20chance%20of%20the%20cancer%20spreading%2C%20a%20routine%20ultrasound%20two%20days%20before%20Thanksgiving%20revealed%20more%20than%2012%20suspicious%20lesions%20on%20my%20liver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20sisters%20frantically%20texted%20Nick%2C%20suggesting%20he%20postpone%20the%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20doesn't%20change%20a%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20them.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20still%20the%20girl%20I%20want%20to%20marry.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nick%20is%20kneeling%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20proposing%20to%20Katie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7b2face7f1785b2e34124%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22682%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%20proposed%20to%20Katie%20on%20Thanksgiving%202014%2C%20surrounded%20by%20family.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Ortman%20Doble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20day%20he%20proposed%20was%20the%20most%20emotional%20day%20of%20my%20life.%20The%20week%20following%2C%20I%20got%20confirmation%20that%20the%20melanoma%20had%20spread%20and%20that%20I%20had%2016%20months%20to%20live.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20filled%20with%20conflicting%20emotions.%20Being%20given%20a%20Stage%204%2C%20incurable%20cancer%20diagnosis%20with%20a%2016-month%20shelf%20life%20is%20pure%20terror.%20Being%20asked%20to%20spend%20forever%2C%20however%20long%20that%20might%20be%2C%20with%20the%20man%20you%20love%20is%20pure%20joy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20felt%20hopeless%20and%20hopeful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222397%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katie%20and%20Nick%20in%20their%20wedding%20clothes%20on%20a%20snowy%20bridge.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ac9090413ab8e1d62e1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%20and%20Katie%20were%20married%20on%20February%2022%2C%202015%2C%20in%20Denver.%3Cp%3EKimi%20D%20Photography%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EPlaying%20whack-a-mole%20with%20my%20cancer%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20first%20oncologist%20told%20me%20I%20had%20only%20one%20treatment%20option%2C%20which%20basically%20guaranteed%20I%20wouldn't%20live%20to%20see%2035%2C%20my%20physician%20father%20spent%20every%20waking%20moment%20trying%20to%20find%20us%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fdoctor-cancer-clinical-trials-advocacy_n_646515dbe4b0bfd6447f88df%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclinical%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20would%20offer%20more%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20more%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENick%20and%20I%20busied%20ourselves%20by%20moving%20in%20together.%20In%20January%202015%2C%20I%20enrolled%20in%20my%20first%20clinical%20trial%20at%20Memorial%20Sloan%20Kettering%20(MSK)%20in%20Manhattan%20for%20five%20weeks.%20By%20February%2C%20we%20were%20married%20in%20an%20intimate%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20clinical%20trial%20at%20MSK%20stabilized%20my%20tumors%20for%20eight%20months.%20When%20I%20experienced%20tumor%20growth%20that%20eliminated%20me%20from%20the%20trial%2C%20I%20enrolled%20in%20my%20second%20trial%20in%20Denver.%20This%20game%20of%20whack-a-mole%20would%20continue%20over%20the%20course%20of%20seven%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20enrolled%20in%20four%20clinical%20trials%2C%20had%20two%20liver%20embolizations%2C%20a%20gamma%20knife%20when%20it%20spread%20to%20my%20brain%2C%20a%20laparoscopic%20liver%20resection%20procedure%2C%20and%20surgery%20to%20remove%20half%20of%20my%20liver.%20Each%20trial%20and%20treatment%20bought%20Nick%20and%20me%20more%20time%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nick%20and%20Katie%20kiss%20in%20matching%20Superman%20t-shirts%20as%20Nick%20shaves%20Katie's%20head.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7b355ce7f1785b2e34165%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%20shaved%20Katie's%20head%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%202016.%20Afterwards%2C%20Nick%20and%20Katie's%20nephew%20Tommy%20buzzed%20their%20hair%2C%20followed%20by%20her%20brothers%2C%20father%2C%20and%20father-in-law%20in%20solidarity.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Ortman%20Doble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20never%20gave%20up%20hope%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20spent%20our%2030s%20in%20fight%20or%20flight%20mode%2C%20but%20we%20never%20gave%20up%20hope.%20We%20continued%20to%20make%20plans.%20We%20built%20a%20house%2C%20we%20got%20a%20puppy%2C%20and%20we%20traveled%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katie%20and%20Nick%20at%20the%20Cliffs%20of%20Moher%20in%20County%20Clare%2C%20Ireland.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ad9f6080194819f984af%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENick%20and%20Katie%20visited%20her%20happy%20place%2C%20the%20Cliffs%20of%20Moher%20in%20County%20Clare%2C%20Ireland%2C%20in%202016.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Ortman%20Doble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20both%20maintained%20our%20careers%2C%20although%20I%20did%20take%20a%20much-needed%20break%20from%20my%20job%20and%20LinkedIn%20networking%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20at%20the%20height%20of%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20enrolled%20in%20my%20fourth%20clinical%20trial%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pittsburgh%20Medical%20Center%20in%20Pennsylvania.%20I%20responded%20very%20well%20to%20the%20treatment%2C%20but%20one%20tumor%20went%20rogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20year%2C%20my%20doctor%20surgically%20removed%20it%20and%20all%20of%20the%20remaining%20cancer%2C%20rendering%20me%20NED%20%E2%80%94%20no%20evidence%20of%20disease.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Katie%20wearing%20a%20tiara%20and%20holding%20balloons%20that%20say%20%26quot%3BNED%26quot%3B%20alongside%20Nick%20and%20their%20dog%2C%20Alice.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65d7ae0a6080194819f984d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20family%20threw%20me%20a%20%26quot%3BNED%26quot%3B%20party%20in%20October%202021.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Ortman%20Doble%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EUnexpected%20connections%20can%20end%20up%20sustaining%20us%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20Nick%20and%20I%20celebrate%20nine%20years%20of%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeeting%20on%20LinkedIn%20over%2010%20years%20ago%20was%20unexpected%20for%20both%20of%20us.%20I%20also%20never%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20that%202%25%20of%20having%20my%20cancer%20spread.%20I'm%20not%20sure%20I%20expected%20to%20be%20here%20now%2C%20but%20life%20has%20a%20way%20of%20surprising%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20not%20suggesting%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flinkedin-is-a-dating-app-remote-work-online-romance-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eusing%20LinkedIn%20as%20a%20dating%20app%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20we%20go%20through%20life%20making%20connections%20with%20strangers.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20when%20we%20least%20expect%20it%2C%20those%20chance%20connections%20end%20up%20sustaining%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3