C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20all%20seeing%20for%20the%20last%20two%20to%20two-and-half%20months%20that%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20received%20summons%20from%20the%20ED%20(Enforcement%20Directorate)%20seven%20times.%20But%20now%20the%20BJP-led%20centre%20has%20understood%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20through%20the%20ED.%20So%20now%20the%20BJP-led%20centre%20is%20bringing%20the%20CBI%20and%20planning%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20through%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20press%20address%20by%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20the%20last%20two%20days%20in%20which%20the%20party%20has%20claimed%20that%20it%20has%20been%20informed%20that%20if%20it%20ties%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%2C%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20arrested%20in%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAtishi%E2%80%99s%20press%20conferences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2022%20too%2C%20Atishi%20addressed%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20which%20she%20had%20also%20said%20that%20if%20seat%20sharing%20arrangements%20proceed%20with%20the%20Congress%20then%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20arrested%20by%20both%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED.%20At%20today%E2%80%99s%20press%20conference%2C%20Atishi%20was%20joined%20by%20AAP%20MP%20Sandeep%20Pathak%20and%20AAP%20MLA%20Saurabh%20Bharadwaj%20where%20they%20reiterated%20that%20they%20have%20learnt%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%E2%80%99s%20plans%20to%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20from%20%E2%80%9Creliable%20sources.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22hi%5C%22%3EBJP%20%E0%A4%B8%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%9A%E0%A4%BE%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%A4%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%E0%A4%82%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A4%BF%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20%E0%A4%9C%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%94%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A4%AE%20%