ia-news%2Fafter-delhi-aap-congress-seal-seat-deal-for-goa-haryana-gujarat-sources-5105903%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethree%20of%20Delhi's%20seven%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20also%20reached%20out%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20Trinamool%20to%20restart%20talks%20that%20fell%20through%20last%20month%20after%20the%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20refused%20to%20budge%20from%20her%20offer%20-%20two%20of%20the%20state's%2042%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20sources%20told%20NDTV%20the%20party%20had%20lowered%20its%20ask%20to%20five%20seats%20-%20but%20a%20Trinamool%20spokesperson%20played%20that%20down%2C%20declaring%20%26quot%3BEven%20with%20binoculars%20we%20are%20unable%20to%20find%20a%20third%20seat%20for%20Congress%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcongress-trinamool-lok-sabha-seat-sharing-india-alliance-even-with-binoculars-trinamool-sources-on-congress-5-seat-demand-5111577%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BEven%20With%20Binoculars...%26quot%3B%3A%20Trinamool%20Sources%20On%20Congress'%205-Seat%20Demand%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20INDIA%20allies%20are%20understood%20to%20have%20differences%20over%20eight%20seats%2C%20including%20two%20in%20Mumbai%20-%20South%20Central%20and%20North%20West%20-%20that%20the%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20Congress%20both%20want.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20delay%20over%20demands%20by%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20boss%20Prakash%20Ambedkar%2C%20who%20wants%20five%20seats%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%20Mr%20Ambedkar's%20party%20contested%2047%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20election%20but%20failed%20to%20win%20any.%20The%20VBA%20also%20contested%20236%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20election%20and%20did%20not%20open%20its%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sena%20(then%20undivided%20and%20allied%20with%20t