m%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChurch%20official%20S.%20Prim%20Vaiphei%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20evacuated%2C%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20our%20houses%20is%20happening%20under%20the%20noses%20of%20Imphal%20East%20district%20administration%20and%20central%20security%20forces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVaiphei%20said%20this%20was%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20order%20telling%20the%20authorities%20to%20safeguard%20the%20properties%20of%20those%20displaced%20due%20to%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20began%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-new-lambulances-last-kuki-families%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20last%20Kuki%20families%20who%20remained%20in%20Imphal%2C%20in%20the%20New%20Lambulane%20area%2C%20had%20accused%20the%20authorities%20of%20forcibly%20evacuating%20them%20on%20September%202%20last%20year.%20A%20total%20of%2024%20individuals%20from%20the%20Kuki%20community%20were%20evacuated%20from%20New%20Lambulane%20on%20that%20day%2C%20including%20infants%20and%20people%20in%20need%20of%20regular%20hospital%20checkups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImphal%20East%20DSP%20K.%20Meghachandra%20Singh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethat%20the%20police%20had%20taken%20steps%20to%20stop%20the%20takeover%20of%20properties%20after%20%E2%80%9Creceiving%20inputs%20about%20some%20people%20trying%20to%20take%20over%20some%20abandoned%20houses%20in%20New%20Lambulane%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20people%20say%20they%20have%20been%20living%20in%20relief%20camps%20and%20want%20to%20shift%20to%20better%20places%20such%20as%20abandoned%20houses.%20We%20sent%20officers%20to%20the%20location%20and%20did%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20do%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20police%20was%20carrying%20out%20a%20survey%20to%20see%20if%20any%20abandoned%20houses%20were%20being%20illegally%20occupied.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708672339000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F28193956%2Fimage-1180.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fimphals-kuki-residents-who-were-evacuated-say-homes-taken-over-by-militia%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Police%20say%20they%20are%20taking%20action%20against%20the%20illegal%20occupation%20of%20abandoned%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fimphals-kuki-residents-who-were-evacuated-say-homes-taken-over-by-militia%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Double%20Murder%2C%20Missing%20TV%20Host%2C%20Killer%20Cop%20In%20Sensational%20Australia%20Crime%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAustralian%20police%20on%20Friday%20charged%20one%20of%20their%20own%20officers%20with%20the%20double%20murder%20of%20a%20TV%20presenter%20and%20his%20flight%20attendant%20boyfriend%2C%20whose%20bodies%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetective%20Superintendent%20Danny%20Doherty%20said%20a%2028-year-old%20serving%20police%20constable%20was%20charged%20with%20two%20counts%20of%20murder%2C%20after%20a%20high-profile%20three-day%20search%20across%20Sydney.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20chance%20discovery%20of%20bloodied%20clothes%20in%20a%20suburban%20rubbish%20bin%20led%20detectives%20to%20the%20home%20of%20former%20red%20carpet%20host%20and%20entertainment%20journalist%20Jesse%20Baird%2C%2026.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20searching%20Baird's%20inner-city%20flat%2C%20detectives%20said%20they%20found%20%26quot%3Ba%20large%20amount%20of%20blood%26quot%3B%20and%20held%20%26quot%3Bgrave%20concerns%26quot%3B%20for%20both%20him%20and%20his%20boyfriend%2C%20Qantas%20flight%20attendant%20Luke%20Davies%2C%2029.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pair%20are%20presumed%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20projectile%20found%20at%20the%20apartment%20matched%20that%20of%20a%20police-issue%20firearm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weapon%20has%20since%20been%20found%20inside%20a%20police%20station%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20officer%20was%20said%20to%20have%20been%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Baird%20until%20recently%2C%20when%20it%20ended%20badly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBaird%20had%20been%20a%20presenter%20on%20Australia's%20Network%20Ten.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%20the%20officer%20turned%20himself%20in%20to%20Bondi%20Police%20Station%2C%20near%20the%20country's%20famed%20beach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFootage%20of%20the%20arrest%20shows%20him%20handcuffed%20and%20escorted%20into%20the%20building%20wearing%20a%20dark%20baseball%20cap%20and%20sneakers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20remains%20in%20custody%20and%20police%20will%20oppose%20granting%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAustralian%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20suspect%20had%20been%20a%20celebrity%20chaser%20and%20blogger%20before%20joining%20the%20police%20force%2C%20and%20had%20been%20photographed%20with%20Taylor%20Swift%2C%20Miley%20Cyrus%2C%20Lady%20Gaga%2C%20Ben%20Stiller%20and%20scores%20of%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20previously%20investigated%20over%20the%20aggressive%20tasering%20of%20an%20Aboriginal%20man%20in%202020%2C%20after%20video%20of%20the%20incident%20emerged%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20reports%20from%202014%20indicate%20that%20he%20came%20out%20publicly%20as%20gay%20by%20throwing%20a%20letter%20onstage%20at%20a%20Lady%20Gaga%20concert%2C%20which%20the%20star%20read%20out%20to%20a%20crowd%20that%20included%20his%20sister.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCharges%20have%20been%20submitted%20for%20two%20counts%20of%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doherty%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20police%20focus%20was%20now%20on%20locating%20the%20bodies%20of%20the%20two%20missing%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20allege%20the%20remains%20of%20the%20two%20men%20were%20transported%20in%20a%20white%20van%20and%20disposed%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForensic%20examinations%20of%20the%20van%20are%20ongoing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20really%20important%20that%20we%20do%20locate%20the%20bodies%2C%20not%20only%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20but%20also%20for%20answers%20for%20the%20family%20who%20are%20grieving%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Doherty.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708672080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fvbtg7ir_australia-anchor_625x300_23_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjesse-baird-luke-davies-double-murder-missing-tv-host-killer-cop-in-sensational-australia-crime-5111547%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Australian%20police%20on%20Friday%20charged%20one%20of%20their%20own%20officers%20with%20the%20double%20murder%20of%20a%20TV%20presenter%20and%20his%20flight%20attendant%20boyfriend%2C%20whose%20bodies%20have%20yet%20to%20be%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjesse-baird-luke-davies-double-murder-missing-tv-host-killer-cop-in-sensational-australia-crime-5111547%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjesse-baird-luke-davies-double-murder-missing-tv-host-killer-cop-in-sensational-australia-crime-5111547%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjesse-baird-luke-davies-double-murder-missing-tv-host-killer-cop-in-sensational-australia-crime-5111547%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Emboldened%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Russia%20marks%20patriotic%20holiday%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708671834000%2C