%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-blocs-up-seat-sharing-pact-finalised-congress-to-fight-on-17-seats-5100395%5C%22%3EI.N.D.I.A%20alliance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20be%20deeply%20disappointed.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dm8Nivzul5JI%5C%22%3ECongress%20and%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20(SP)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20after%20much%20suspense%2C%20like%20a%20good%20one-day%20cricket%20match%2C%20have%20reached%20a%20decision%20on%20seat%20distribution.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dvs99xllDQ6c%5C%22%3ECongress%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20contest%2017%20seats%20and%20the%20rest%20will%20be%20fought%20by%20the%20SP%2C%20along%20with%20smaller%20parties.%20The%20Congress%20has%20decided%20to%20give%20one%20more%20seat%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fnews%2Fnews%2Fsamajwadi-party-ups-the-ante-on-congress-releases-second-list-of-candidates-762797%5C%22%3ESP%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20reflects%20that%20the%20grand%20old%20party%20has%20learnt%20its%20lesson%20after%20the%20historic%20debacle%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20Just%20to%20remind%20readers%2C%20during%20those%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Kamal%20Nath%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20had%20attacked%20SP%20chief%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-will-akhilesh-yadav-join-rahul-gandhi-bharat-jodo-yatra-his-condition-for-congress-5085548%5C%22%3EAkhilesh%20Yadav%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20calling%20him%20names%2C%20who%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20angered%20and%20humiliated%2C%20went%20on%20to%20equate%20the%20Congress%20with%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP).%20However%2C%20now%20that%20the%20deal%20is%20sealed%2C%20I%20guess%20we%20can%20say%20all%20is%20well%20that%20ends%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20UP%20Is%20An%20Important%20State%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUttar%20Pradesh%20is%20a%20critical%20state%20for%20any%20party%20or%20political%20formation%20that%20aims%20to%20rule%20at%20the%20centre.%20In%202014%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20selected%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20its%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20contest%20from%20Varanasi%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20Vadodara%20in%20Gujarat.%20In%20fact%2C%20after%20winning%20both%20seats%2C%20he%20chose%20Varanasi%20and%20gave%20up%20Vadodara.%20Modi%20was%20aware%20that%20without%20winning%20a%20substantial%20number%20of%20seats%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20would%20be%20impossible%20to%20fulfil%20his%20lifelong%20aim%20of%20becoming%20the%20PM.%20It's%20no%20coincidence%20that%20the%20BJP%20then%20appointed%20Amit%20Shah%20to%20oversee%20the%20elections%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20party%20ended%20up%20winning%2071%20seats%20out%20of%2080%2C%20while%20its%20ally%20Apna%20Dal%20got%20two.%20What%20surprised%20a%20few%20BJP%20supporters%20was%20the%20fact%20that%20just%20two%20years%20before%20that%2C%20in%20the%202012%20assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20party%20had%20managed%20to%20get%20only%20a%2015%25%20vote%20share.%20But%20the%20Modi-Shah%20pair%20turned%20the%20tables%20on%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%2C%20then%20considered%20the%20principal%20players%20in%20the%20state.%20There%20was%20a%20time%20in%20fact%20when%20the%20BJP%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Congress%2C%20used%20to%20struggle%20for%20the%20third%20and%20the%20fourth%20spot%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20SP-BSP%20Alliance%20In%202019%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20further%20proved%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20emerged%20as%20a%20formidable%20force%20and%20no%20political%20party%20had%20the%20firepower%20to%20defeat%20it%20alone.%20No%20wonder%20then%20that%20in%202019%2C%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20BSP%2C%20who%20had%20always%20been%20bitter%20foes%2C%20decided%20to%20bury%20their%20difference%20and%20join%20forces.%20They%20did%20manage%20to%20win%2015%20seats%20together%2C%20but%20the%20BJP%20still%20captured%20the%20lion's%20share%2C%20along%20with%20an%20enhanced%20vote%20share.%20From%2042%25%20votes%20in%202014%2C%20the%20party%20improved%20its%20tally%20to%2049%25%20by%202019.%20Since%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20successively%20won%20two%20assembly%20elections%2C%20both%20with%20a%20clear%20majority%20and%20with%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20as%20CM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20in%20this%20context%20that%20the%20alliance%20between%20the%20SP%20and%20the%20Congress%20assumes%20importance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EA%20Dwindling%20BSP%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20denying%20the%20fact%20that%20though%20it%20was%20ultimately%20trounced%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20SP%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20polls%20had%20commanded%20an%20impressive%2032%25%20vote%20share%2C%20its%20best-ever%20performance.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20had%20tried%20to%20create%20a%20rainbow%20coalition%20with%20caste-based%20small%20political%20parties%2C%20though%20that%20coalition%20collapsed%20after%20the%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBSP%20chief%20Mayawati%2C%20for%20some%20mysterious%20reason%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20in%20no%20mood%20to%20seriously%20contest%20elections%C2%A0in%202024.%20Her%20party's%20vote%20share%20has%20dropped%20drastically%2C%20and%20she%20has%20already%20announced%20that%20the%20BSP%20would%20fight%20alone.%20Mayawati's%20absence%20from%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20alliance%20is%20advantageous%20to%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%2C%20it%20would%20be%20erroneous%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20this%20time%20is%20no%20match%20for%20the%20BJP's%20might.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20seems%20to%20understand%20this%20very%20well%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EWhy%20The%20BJP%20Is%20Careful%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20attempt%20to%20wean%20away%20the%20Jayant%20Chaudhary-led%20Rashtriya%20Lok%20Dal%20(RLD)%20from%20the%20I.N.D.I.A%20bloc%20underlines%20this.%20Despite%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20party%20seems%20aware%20that%20it%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20repeat%20its%20performance%20of%20the%20last%20two%20general%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20euphoria%20around%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20inauguration%2C%20which%20came%20in%20January%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20on%20a%20decline%20already%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20should%20also%20know%20that%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20temple%20may%20not%20automatically%20reflect%20in%20the%20voting%20behaviour%20of%20people.%20The%20faith%20of%20devotees%20and%20their%20voting%20behaviour%20are%20two%20different%20things.%20One%20can%20feel%20grateful%20towards%20the%20BJP%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple%2C%20but%20to%20be%20certain%20that%20people%20will%20vote%20for%20the%20BJP%20might%20be%20a%20mistake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20does%20not%20want%20to%20take%20chances%20either.%20Two%20incidents%20signify%20this%20argument.%20One%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20consecration%2C%20the%20BJP%20created%20a%20window%20for%20Nitish%20Kumar%20to%20return%20to%20the%20NDA%20-%20this%20was%20a%20party%20that%20had%20publicly%20said%20that%20its%20doors%20were%20shut%20for%20Nitish.%20Two%2C%20it%20announced%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20Karpoori%20Thakur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20also%20announced%20a%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Chaudhary%20Charan%20Singh.%20Singh%20was%20a%20farmer%20leader%20with%20a%20massive%20following%20in%20the%20Jat%20community.%20His%20son%20Ajit%20Singh%20could%20not%20consolidate%20his%20father's%20legacy%2C%20and%20his%20grandson%2C%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%2C%20has%20also%20been%20reduced%20to%20leading%20a%20few%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20through%20the%20RLD.%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%20and%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20used%20to%20be%20on%20good%20terms%20and%20were%20considered%20inseparable%2C%20but%20that%20was%20only%20until%20the%20Bharat%20Ratna%20for%20Charan%20Singh.%20In%20western%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20especially%20in%20Jat-dominated%20areas%2C%20where%20Muslims%20are%20also%20present%20in%20good%20numbers%2C%20the%20BJP%20might%20face%20stiff%20resistance%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EThe%20Farmers'%20Protests%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20farmers%20are%20on%20the%20warpath%20again.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20farmer's%20struggle%2C%20thanks%20to%20Mahendra%20Singh%20Tikait%2C%20has%20had%20a%20huge%20impact%20in%20this%20area.%20During%20the%20last%20agitation%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20to%20withdraw%20the%20three%20contentious%20farm%20laws.%20But%20the%20farmers'%20main%20demands%20remain%20unfulfilled.%20They%20have%20been%20demanding%20that%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20should%20be%20given%20for%20MSP%20(Minimum%20Support%20Price)%20for%20crops%20and%20that%20the%20Swaminathan%20Commission%20recommendations%20be%20honoured%20by%20the%20government.%20Two%20years%20back%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20had%20set%20up%20a%20committee%20to%20study%20this%2C%20but%20even%20after%20over%2035%20sittings%2C%20no%20final%20decision%20has%20been%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20current%20agitation%20continues%2C%20it%20will%20adversely%20impact%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%20in%20the%20area.%20Many%20may%20also%20not%20have%20forgotten%20the%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20incident%20in%202021%2C%20in%20which%20a%20few%20farmers%20were%20mowed%20down%20by%20the%20son%20of%20a%20central%20minister%20and%20the%20government%20failed%20to%20take%20any%20action.%20The%20million-dollar%20question%2C%20is%2C%20will%20Jayant%20prove%20to%20be%20handy%20for%20the%20BJP%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EModi's%20Popularity%20Intact%2C%20But%20There%20Are%20Challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%20is%20the%20most%20popular%20leader%20in%20the%20country.%20His%20image%20as%20a%20Hindutva%20icon%20is%20still%20intact.%20He%20has%20also%20bolstered%20his%20status%20as%20a%20Prime%20Minister%20who%20is%20taking%20the%20country%20on%20a%20strong%20development%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20would%20be%20useful%20to%20remember%20that%20beyond%20the%20grand%20vision%20of%20winning%20370%20seats%2C%2010%20years%20of%20anti-incumbency%C2%A0against%20any%20government%20is%20no%20small%20matter%2C%20and%20no%20leader%20can%20afford%20to%20ignore%20it.%20There%20is%20unprecedented%20unemployment.%20Inflation%20is%20running%20high.%20The%20BJP%20government%20knows%20this%20well%2C%20and%20extending%20free%20ration%20to%2081%20crore%20people%20underlines%20its%20concern.%20In%20this%20context%2C%20the%20alliance%20of%20SP%20and%20the%20Congress%20might%20just%20have%20made%20the%20contest%20a%20bit%20more%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Ashutosh%20is%20the%20author%20of%20'Hindu%20Rashtra'%20and%20Editor%20of%20satyahindi.com.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708668600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F14i3r5do_rahul-gandhi-akhilesh-yadav_625x300_17_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-congress-alliance-5111410%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20would%20be%20erroneous%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20SP-Congress%20alliance%20is%20no%20match%20for%20the%20BJP's%20might%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20BJP%2C%20on%20its%20part%2C%20seems%20to%20understand%20this%20very%20well%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-congress-alliance-5111410%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhy-bjp-should-not-ignore-sp-co