0Service%20Commission)%3C%2Fa%3E%20exams%20stand%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20competitive%20and%20challenging%20examinations%20to%20conquer.%20Behind%20the%20triumph%20of%20many%20rank%20holders%20and%20nearly%20all%20officers%2C%20lies%20a%20compelling%20story%20of%20perseverance%20and%20resilience%20amidst%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20story%20is%20that%20of%20Sonal%20Goel%20%E2%80%94%20an%20IAS%20officer%2C%20currently%20serving%20as%20the%20Resident%20Commissioner%20at%20Tripura%20Bhawan%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20She%20secured%20the%20All%20India%20Rank%2013%20in%20the%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20in%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20many%20know%20that%20this%20was%20her%20second%20attempt%2C%20as%20she%20fell%20short%20of%20going%20to%20the%20interview%20stage%20by%20a%20few%20marks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESonal%20recounted%20this%20story%20alongside%20a%20picture%20of%20her%20UPSC%20Civil%20Services%202007%20Mains%20mark%20sheet%2C%20shared%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20She%20reflected%20on%20the%20trials%20and%20tribulations%20that%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20her%20selection%20in%20May%202008.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20remarkably%2C%20she%20achieved%20this%20feat%20while%20simultaneously%20pursuing%20her%20LLB%20(Bachelor%20of%20Laws)%20and%20working%20part-time%20as%20a%20Company%20Secretary%20(CS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20had%20low%20marks%20in%20the%20general%20studies%20paper%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20qualify%20for%20the%20interview%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20this%20setback%20fueled%20my%20determination%20to%20leave%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20achieving%20my%20goal%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330545%2Fakshay-ridlan-qr-code-locket-finding-lost-missing-people-dementia-autism-upsc%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUPSC%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20devoted%20herself%20to%20mastering%20the%20