tion%5C%22%3ERaghuveer%20designed%20a%20universal%20cap%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%20from%20chemotherapy%20damage.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tackle%20this%20unavoidable%20problem%2C%20Raghuveer%20has%20developed%20a%20unique%20scalp%20cooling%20system%20that%20alleviates%20the%20trauma%20of%20chemotherapy-induced%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F21121%2Fnatural-hair-wigs-cancer-patients-chennai-tangled%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehair%20loss%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Currently%2C%20his%20innovation%20%E2%80%98Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%E2%80%99%20is%20installed%20in%2018%20hospitals%20across%20Telangana%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Kerala%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Delhi.%20He%20says%20more%20than%203%2C000%20successful%20sessions%20have%20been%20conducted%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20sat%20down%20with%20Raghuveer%20to%20understand%20more%20about%20the%20novel%20device%20and%20how%20it%20can%20solve%20one%20of%20chemotherapy%E2%80%99s%20most%20challenging%20side%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20scalp%20cooling%20mechanism%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20engineer%20by%20education%2C%20Raghuveer%20pursued%20his%20higher%20education%20at%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%20Ranchi.%20In%202013%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315492%2Fvadodara-pragmatech-healthcare-solutions-cervicheck-kits-detect-cervical-cancer-at-home%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharmaceutical%20company%20%3C%2Fa%3EPfizer%20and%20later%20worked%20with%20Roche%20where%20he%20was%20a%20launch%20lead%20for%20the%20breast%20cancer%20drug%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20his%20work%20experience%20in%20oncology%2C%20he%20founded%20his%20own%20startup%20%E2%80%98Dignite%E2%80%99%20for%20can