20and%20heading%20off%20to%20work.%20After%20finishing%20work%2C%20she%20faced%20the%20challenging%20task%20of%20gathering%20firewood%20for%20cooking.%20She%20had%20to%20carry%20several%20kilograms%20of%20wood%20on%20her%20head%20as%20she%20made%20her%20way%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342261%2Fwoman-entrepreneur-saroj-prajapati-founder-moms-magic-pickle-mango-madhya-pradesh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eback%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELalita%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20both%20daily%20wage%20labourers%20in%20Badjhir%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Seoni%20district%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ECentre%20for%20Science%20and%20Environment%20(CSE)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20nearly%20500%20million%20people%20in%20India%20lack%20access%20to%20clean%20cooking%20solutions.%20The%20report%20highlights%20that%2041%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population%20%E2%80%94%20including%20individuals%20like%20Lalita%20%E2%80%94%20rely%20on%20biomass%20as%20cooking%20fuel.%20This%20reliance%20contributes%20to%20approximately%20340%20million%20tonnes%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20emissions%2C%20which%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2013%20percent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20total%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20smoke%20from%20fuel%20burned%20for%20heating%20and%20cooking%20is%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20contributors%20to%20indoor%20air%20pollution%20in%20India.%20The%20World%20Health%20Organisation%20(WHO)%20estimates%20that%20every%20year%2C%203.2%20million%20people%20die%20prematurely%20from%20illnesses%20attributable%20to%20household%20air%20pollution%20caused%20by%20the%20incomplete%20combustion%20of%20solid%20fuels%20and%20kerosene%20used%20for%20cooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20long-term%20solution%20for%20this%20is%20the%20usage%20of%20LPG%20stoves%2C%20which%20the%20Government%20is%20providing%20through%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Ujjwala%20Yojana%2C%20many%20are%20yet%20to%20adapt%20to%20it%20as%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20afford%20refills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Ankit%20Mathur%20came%20across%20this%20problem%2C%20fresh%20out%20of%20IIM-Ahmedabad%2C%20in%202008%2C%20he%20started%20looking%20for%20a%20solution%20with%20his%20co-founder%20Neha%20Juneja.%20Interested%20in%20the%20sustainability%20space%2C%20they%20were%20working%20on%20renewable%20energy%20projects%20in%20rural%20areas.%20Here%2C%20they%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20daily%20challenges%20in%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20saw%20that%20most%20of%20the%20women%E2%80%99s%20time%20was%20spent%20either%20cooking%20or%20collecting%20firewood%20to%20cook.%20After%20observing%20the%20amount%20of%20smoke%20emanating%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3Echulhas%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20studying%20its%20detrimental%20effects%20on%20health%2C%20the%20duo%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20a%20clean%20cooking%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20of%20research%20across%20various%20states%20and%20several%20prototypes%20later%2C%20they%20built%20the%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20a%20single-burner%2C%20high-efficiency%20cook%20stove%20that%20reduces%20smoke.%20Since%202012%2C%20Greenway%20Grameen%20Infra%20has%20sold%20three%20million%20cookstoves%20and%20wants%20to%20make%20clean%20cooking%20accessible%20to%20every%20part%20of%20rural%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EProviding%20access%20to%20clean%20energy%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-13-1708433713.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greenway%20has%20provided%20clean%20energy%20to%20over%203%20million%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the