%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20went%20out%20looking%20for%20help%2C%20all%20he%20found%20was%20an%20overpriced%20option.%20This%20led%20to%20the%20foundation%20of%20Ambitio%20%E2%80%94%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20AI%20admissions%20platform%2C%20to%20help%20applicants%20secure%20admissions%20to%20top%20global%20universities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirghayu%20explains%20in%20detail%20how%20Ambitio%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340888%2Fshark-tank-cybersecurity-app-artificial-intelligence-ai-pratyusha-vemuri-online-fraud-transactions%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euses%20AI%20to%20help%20students%20%3C%2Fa%3Esecure%20admissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENot%20his%20first%20try%20at%20entrepreneurship%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20completing%20his%20graduation%20from%20IIT-BHU%2C%20Dirghayu%20Kaushik%20got%20a%20job%20in%20a%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20got%20hired%20as%20a%20founding%20member%20in%20a%20startup.%20For%20about%20two%20years%2C%20I%20spearheaded%20their%20entire%20product%20development%2C%20overseeing%20the%20creation%20of%20both%20the%20tech%20and%20product%20teams%20from%20scratch.%20We%20started%20with%20just%20a%20four-member%20team%2C%20including%20the%20founders%2C%20and%20expanded%20significantly%20during%20my%20tenure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20he%20was%20working%20at%20the%20startup%2C%20he%20was%20also%20looking%20for%20colleges%20to%20further%20his%20education.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20completed%20my%20graduation%20and%20started%20to%20look%20for%20foreign%20universities%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20MBA.%20The%20process%20was%20tedious%20and%20I%20realised%20that%20there%20was%20no%20platform%20to%20help%20students%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20counsellors%20who%20help%20students%20get%20into%20universities%20but%20they%20charge%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20which%20might%20not%20be%20affordable%20to%20everyone.%20Additionally%2C%20they%20can%20help%20you%20with%20particular%20college%20admission%20and%20not%20with%20a%20variety%20of%20colleges%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirghayu%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20platform%20that%20did%20it%20all%20for%20students%20%E2%80%94%20college%20applications%2C%20personal%20essays%2C%20and%20finding%20the%20right%20college%20for%20the%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20went%20to%20my%20college%20buddies%20%E2%80%94%20Vikrant%20Shivalik%20and%20Vaibhav%20Tyagi%20%E2%80%94%20and%20told%20them%20about%20my%20idea.%20They%20were%20enthralled%20and%20we%20joined%20hands%20to%20create%20the%20platform%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20founders%20of%20Ambitio.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fabcf-12-1708005010-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341975%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20founders%20of%20Ambitio.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trio%20developed%20the%20platform%20and%20launched%20it%20in%202023.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20began%20by%20assemblin